    public abstract class BaseHeapDomain<H extends BaseHeapDomain<H>>
extends BaseLattice<H>
implements HeapDomain<H>
    A base implementation of the HeapDomain interface, handling base cases of smallStepSemantics(SymbolicExpression). All implementers of HeapDomain should inherit from this class for ensuring a consistent behavior on the base cases, unless explicitly needed.
